            <h1 align=“center”>Basic Composition Skill Sharing</h1>
             <h2>1.What is composition?</h2>
                 <h3>1.1 Definiton</h3>
                     <p>All the <mark>ways arranging object in a pianting or photograph</mark> can be called as Composition.</p>
                 <h3>1.2 Function</h3>
                     <p>Composition can <mark>enhances effect in your painting or photograph</mark>, such as enhancing lonely/empty by leaving space, opposing by unbalance and peaceful by balance. They can help you express the conception of your painting or photograph.</p>
            <h2>2.Composition Skills</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Balance</li>
